LanguageData.AlertCantClaimBedDesc:
These guests can't afford to claim a suite:

{0}
Provide cheaper or complimentary suites or gift the guests some silver. Better-connected factions tend to arrive with fuller purses.

LanguageData.AlertHasNoFoodDesc:
These guests have nothing to eat:

{0}
Put food on sale, stock a refreshment kiosk, or gift the guests some silver or rations. You can also allow guests to dine for free.
